CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

December 15, 2006

[Cite as 12/1512006 Case Announcements, 2006-0hio-6602.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1000. Colonial Village Ltd. v. Washington Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2004-A-574. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellees’ motion to dismiss appeal,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
